<h3>Bidders conference and tender competition</h3>
<p>Following the bidders conference held in May 2015, the tender competition was reduced to a shortlist of preferred bidders for Down Street. Our Operational Business department have since been working with these organisations to establish the feasibility and cost of the schemes. </p>
<p>Once we have a decision about Down Street we can proceed, and begin to consider the options for other unique, disused sites on the network.&nbsp; </p>
<p>To register interest in any of our disused stations, please email <a href="mailto:disusedstations&#64;tfl.gov.uk">disusedstations&#64;tfl.gov.uk</a>. </p>
